  "body_html": "<!DOCTYPE html\n  SYSTEM \"about:legacy-compat\">\n<html lang=\"en-us\" dir=\"ltr\"><head><title>Securities Account List</title><meta charset=\"utf-8\"><link rel=\"stylesheet\" type=\"text/css\" media=\"screen,projection\" href=\"/resource/css/style-v2.css\"><script type=\"text/javascript\" src=\"js/sap-strings.js\"></script></head><body class=\"en-us sap-light centered navigation-default enumeration-disabled\"><div id=\"d4h5-main-container\" class=\"container_12\" role=\"application\"><div id=\"d4h5-section-container\" class=\"grid_12\"><div id=\"d4h5-main-content\" class=\"grid_8 alpha omega\"><section><div class=\"page topic  - topic-topic \" id=\"loio64f2c753b1081d4be10000000a174cb4\"><h1 class=\"title topictitle1\">Securities Account List </h1><div class=\"body\">\n<div class=\"section\"><section class=\"section\" type=\"Use\"><h2 class=\"section_title\">Use</h2>\n<p class=\"p\"> You can use the securities account list to display master data and payment information for one, several or all securities accounts in a company code. You can also print this information.\n</p>\n<p class=\"p\"> The list is displayed using the <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">SAP List Viewer</span> .\n</p>\n<p class=\"p\"><span class=\"ph emphasis emphasis\">See also:</span>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p\"><a class=\"xref\" href=\"4dd40b7ac2234be2e10000000a42189c.html\" title=\"\">SAP List Viewer for SAP GUI (Classic)</a>\n</p>\n</section></div>\n<div class=\"section\"><section class=\"section\" type=\"Activities\"><h2 class=\"section_title\">Activities</h2>\n<ol class=\"ol\"><li class=\"li\"><p class=\"p\">Choose either <span class=\"ph menucascade\"><img src=\"themes/sap-light/img/navstart.gif\" alt=\"Start of the navigation path\" title=\"Start of the navigation path\"><span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Information System</span>&nbsp;<img src=\"themes/sap-light/img/navstep.gif\" alt=\"Next navigation step\" title=\"Next navigation step\">&nbsp;<span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Master Data</span>&nbsp;<img src=\"themes/sap-light/img/navstep.gif\" alt=\"Next navigation step\" title=\"Next navigation step\">&nbsp;<span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Securities Account</span>&nbsp;<img src=\"themes/sap-light/img/navstep.gif\" alt=\"Next navigation step\" title=\"Next navigation step\">&nbsp;<span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Securities Account List</span><img src=\"themes/sap-light/img/navend.gif\" alt=\"End of the navigation path\" title=\"End of the navigation path\"></span> or <span class=\"ph menucascade\"><img src=\"themes/sap-light/img/navstart.gif\" alt=\"Start of the navigation path\" title=\"Start of the navigation path\"><span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Securities</span>&nbsp;<img src=\"themes/sap-light/img/navstep.gif\" alt=\"Next navigation step\" title=\"Next navigation step\">&nbsp;<span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Master Data</span>&nbsp;<img src=\"themes/sap-light/img/navstep.gif\" alt=\"Next navigation step\" title=\"Next navigation step\">&nbsp;<span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Securities Account</span>&nbsp;<img src=\"themes/sap-light/img/navstep.gif\" alt=\"Next navigation step\" title=\"Next navigation step\">&nbsp;<span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Securities Account List.</span><img src=\"themes/sap-light/img/navend.gif\" alt=\"End of the navigation path\" title=\"End of the navigation path\"></span>\n</p></li><li class=\"li\"><p class=\"p\"> Enter the <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Company code</span> .\n</p></li><li class=\"li\"><p class=\"p\"> By making entries in the fields below, you can select the securities accounts you want to see.\n</p><ol class=\"ol\" type=\"a\"><li class=\"li\"><p class=\"p\"><span class=\"ph uicontrol\"> Securities Account</span>\n</p></li><li class=\"li\"><p class=\"p\"><span class=\"ph uicontrol\"> Securities Account Type</span>\n</p></li><li class=\"li\"><p class=\"p\"><span class=\"ph uicontrol\"> Securities Account Category</span>\n</p></li><li class=\"li\"><p class=\"p\"><span class=\"ph uicontrol\"> Portfolio</span>\n</p></li><li class=\"li\"><p class=\"p\"><span class=\"ph uicontrol\"> Depository Bank</span>\n</p></li><li class=\"li\"><p class=\"p\"><span class=\"ph uicontrol\"> Beneficiary</span>\n</p><p class=\"p\"> If you do not enter any other selection criteria, the system displays all the securities accounts in the company code.\n</p></li></ol></li><li class=\"li\"><p class=\"p\"> Choose <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Execute.</span>\n</p></li><li class=\"li\"><p class=\"p\"> The securities account list is generated according to the selections made.\n</p></li></ol>\n</section></div>\n</div></div></section><div class=\"clear\"></div>\n</div></div></div></body></html>"
}